Classifier: Programming Language :: Python :: 3
Classifier: Operating System :: Linux
Description-Content-Type: text/plain

python3-bigbluebutton is a Python 3 module (and some scripts) to work
with a Big Blue Button video conferencing system.

Usage of the module:

    import bigbluebutton

Available scripts:

    bbb-get-meetings
    bbb-shared-notes
